DOC.brief_summary: The objective of the current trial is to evaluate safety, tolerability and pharmacokinetics of multiple rising doses of BI 113608 in healthy male volunteers
DOC.brief_title: Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics of Multiple Rising Doses of BI 113608 in Healthy Male Volunteers
DOC.criteria: Inclusion criteria: 1. healthy male subjects Exclusion criteria: 1. Any relevant deviation from healthy conditions
